{"tid":2287253,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普宣布國家進入緊急狀態 應對中共威脅|","createTime":"2020-11-15T15:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T23:27:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6e9c9bd2473cae7e45145bef49330e62babfb6a7","tid":2287253,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:00:38.000Z","msg":"HONG KONG<br />\n<br />\n特朗普宣布國家進入緊急狀態 應對中共威脅| <br />\n#香港大紀元新唐人聯合新聞頻道<br />\nNov 15, 2020<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FWpUaHaN68I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFWpUaHaN68I&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3tqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=a845ddb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FWpUaHaN68I</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港大紀元新唐人聯合新聞頻道<br />\n410K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n【時事焦點】美國總統特朗普週五（11月13日）給眾議院議長和參議院議長發出一封公開信，指出他已經宣布國家進入緊急狀態（National Emergency），以應對來自中共的威脅。白宮在其官方網站上公布了這封信。<br />\n<br />\n公開信中說：「根據《國際緊急狀態經濟權力法》（International Emergency Economic Powers Act）、《國家緊急狀態法》（National Emergencies Act）和《美利堅合眾國法典》（United States Code），我在此報告，我已頒布一項（總統）行政命令，宣布全國進入緊急狀態，以應對來自中國（中共）的威脅。中共為促進軍事、情報和其他安全機構的發展和現代化，對美國資本的攫取日益增長。繼續允許中國（中共）通過包括發展和部署大規模殺傷性武器、先進常規武器，以及針對美國及其人民的惡意網絡行動等途徑，直接威脅美國本土和海外美國軍隊。」<br />\n發佈日期：2020年11月15日<br />\n責任編輯：Simon<br />\n<br />\n香港大紀元邁向20年，參加【和你寫生日卡】💌贊助活動：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/34wpQUN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F34wpQUN&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3tqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=3dedcc37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/34wpQUN</a><br />\n<br />\n這個是需要真相的時代，也是一個需要正義的時代。香港大紀元與新唐人一直站在赤紅色的土地上，對抗極權，不斷受到打壓。如果大家支持我們媒體，增加我們影響力及製作更多高質素節目，可以幫助我們💪🏻：<br />\n<br />\n✅讚好、留言及分享<br />\n✅首播Live Chat時直接打賞<br />\n✅YouTube的廣告完整看完 <br />\n✅直接贊助大紀元：<a href=\"https://www.epochtimeshk.org/sponsors\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimeshk.org%2Fsponsors&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3tqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=a368b004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimeshk.org/sponsors</a><br />\n✅成為我們的Patron: <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/epochtimeshk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fepochtimeshk&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3tqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=4167bc38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/epochtimeshk</a><br />\n✅網站新聞訂閱：<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/subscribe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fsubscribe&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3tqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=51fdae1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/subscribe</a><br />\n💎立即成為大紀元會員：<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/subscribe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fsubscribe&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3tqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=51fdae1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/subscribe</a><br />\n每月只需2杯☕☕價錢前線記者們就可以堅持下去！"},{"pid":"e16331a9fa1d13aba8c2ef2e1ffe6505e5c50274","tid":2287253,"uid":67468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd6d8e8f25e0e2b89ca4631e0c516da10c7a39b","tid":2287253,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:05:21.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"4b8202ae05f3892654dc2dc3c5cdc43e498952a3","tid":2287253,"uid":106408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:11:28.000Z","msg":"對中國 耍君子打嘴仗係冇用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5407e00d55b8fbf863adfe77c419ee10a6d7563b","tid":2287253,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T23:25:20.000Z","msg":"then ??"},{"pid":"b850ca2cdf0a7c470af36796201db76f13db137e","tid":2287253,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T23:26:13.000Z","msg":"又係大妓院<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5a574413bd1d38dca3e052e